The Queen of the Will-o'-the-wisps
Will-o'-the-wisps who can kill anyone in their vicinity with their fire are said to breed in a ravine to the north of Dead City. You must kill their Queen who helps these dangerous entities multiply.
#subobj  1
Find the entrance to the ravine
The entrance to the ravine is in the mountains to the north of the main Dead City gates.
#subobj  2
Find the Queen of the Will-o'-the-wisps
The Queen of the Will-o'-the-wisps can be found deep in the ravine.
#subobj  3
Kill the Queen of the Will-o'-the-wisps
If you do not kill the Queen of the Will-o'-the-wisps, it will be ever more dangerous to move around Gipath..
